name: cleopatra
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cleopatra" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/MAfarrag/cleopatra/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ab6c701bda6498d6ac28c1d72fe13c75d8a68cf91087a44137217ef8954e0ffe

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python  >=3.7.1,<3.10
    - pip >=21.3.1
  run:
    - python  >=3.7.1,<3.10
    - pip >=21.3.1
    - numpy >=1.21.2,<1.22.4
    - matplotlib-base >=3.4.2,<3.6.0

test:
  imports:
    - cleopatra

about:
  home: https://github.com/MAfarrag/cleopatra
  license:  GPL-3.0-only
  license_family: GPL
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: matplotlib utility package
  description: |
    matplotlib utility package.
  dev_url: https://github.com/MAfarrag/cleopatra
  doc_url: https://cleopatra.readthedocs.io/
  doc_source_url: https://github.com/MAfarrag/cleopatra/main/README.md

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - MAfarrag
